        <abstract>
            <p>The die is cast on Ayrton affair. Lord Derby has called for all of the correspondence, as a result of pressure by men of science on JDH’s behalf.</p>
            <p>Has just had a Greenland collection, which supports his views altogether; "I am ready to do fight for these with you."</p>
        </abstract>
